('000000000009','It’s ok for the government to look at photos that I’ve posted publicly on a website, but I don’t want the government to see private photos on my phone, computer, cloud storage or other medium where I have a reasonable sense of privacy.','9','000000000055',1,'','','2015-05-01 00:00:00', '0', '2015-05-01 00:00:00', '0', 0),
